@EnrollmentSystem.GradeService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5003
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{EnrollmentSystem.GradeService_HostAddress}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Student Grades (Replace 1 with actual student ID)
GET {{EnrollmentSystem.GradeService_HostAddress}}/api/grades/student/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Course Grades (Faculty only - Replace 1 with actual course ID)
GET {{EnrollmentSystem.GradeService_HostAddress}}/api/grades/course/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Upload Grade (Faculty only)
POST {{EnrollmentSystem.GradeService_HostAddress}}/api/grades/upload
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": 1,
  "courseId": 1,
  "numericGrade": 95.5,
  "letterGrade": "A"
}

###
